summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3533, for the improvement of 15th Avenue West, from West Nickerson Street to Elliott Avenue West; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, under Ordinance No. 43667, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
